    credentials.id = ++_totalSupply;
    _credMap[issuer] = credentials;
    emit IssuedCredentials(issuer, to, credentials);
}
```

Burnling a credential requires the caller to provide the `id` of the credential to be burnt. The smart contract can then verify the owner of the credential and burn it from the mapping.

```solidity
