The transfer function would allow an owner to transfer its credentials to another address. The contract can then update the `owner` field in the corresponding `credentials` mapping.

```solidity
function transferCredentials(address to, uint256 tokenId) public {
    Credentials memory credentials = _credMap[msg.sender];
    require(credentials.owner == msg.sender, "Not owner");
